panels.description: Writes bytes (per second), actually sent to server

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX_io_writes_server_bytes_per_second") AS "MAX", MEAN("MEAN_io_writes_server_bytes_per_second") AS "Mean", MEAN("MEDIAN_io_writes_server_bytes_per_second") AS "Median", MIN("MIN_io_writes_server_bytes_per_second") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."io_mount_nfs" WHERE ${timeFilter} AND "path" =~ /^${Export}$/ GROUP BY time(${__interval})
